  <h1>Easy-Tips Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Effective Date: February 6, 2025</p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    Easy-Tips (“the App”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our app. By using the App, you consent to the practices described in this policy.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Personal Information:</strong> When using the app, Apple may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and payment details if you choose to upgrade to a paid version of the app.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Location Information:</strong> We collect your location data to automatically populate the merchant’s name, address, and phone number at the time of your transaction.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Spending Data:</strong> The app collects and stores the details of your spendings, including the amount, date, and location of the transaction, as well as the merchant’s information.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Advertising Data:</strong> The app uses Google AdMob for advertisements. Google may collect information such as your device ID, browsing activity, and other app usage data to provide personalized ads. Please refer to Google’s AdMob privacy policy for more information.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Pro Feature Data Collection:</strong> If you use the Pro feature, we may collect additional data to improve the accuracy of pre-tax tip calculations and enhance app functionality. This includes, but is not limited to:
      <ul>
        <li>Device Information: To optimize app performance on different devices and enhance tip calculation logic.</li>
        <li>Location Information: Used to determine appropriate tax rates and tipping recommendations.</li>
        <li>Transaction Details: Information about transactions, such as subtotal amounts before tax and merchant info, to refine the accuracy of tip calculations.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Split Payment Data Collection:</strong> If you use the Split Payment feature, we may collect certain transaction details to generate a Venmo-compatible payment link. This includes:
      <ul>
        <li>Venmo ID (if entered by the user).</li>
        <li>Payment amount and merchant details.</li>
      </ul>
      These details are used only to create a Venmo payment link for your convenience.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Zelle Data Collection:</strong> If you choose to enter Zelle information in the app, this data is:
      <ul>
        <li>Stored only on your Apple iCloud account and device for convenience.</li>
        <li>Not stored on Easy-Tips servers and not accessed by us.</li>
        <li>Used exclusively within the App to help facilitate transactions.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Sharing via Split Payment:</strong> If you use Split Payment, your Venmo/Zelle details and transaction details such as merchant information and transaction date/amount may be shared with other users you designate. Easy-Tips does not control or monitor how this information is shared.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Track and display your spending history.</li>
    <li>Auto-populate merchant information based on your location at the time of purchase.</li>
    <li>Provide personalized advertising via Google AdMob.</li>
    <li>Improve the app and add new features, including enhancing the accuracy of Pro feature pre-tax tip calculations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
  <p>We may share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Google AdMob: For advertising purposes. Google collects data to provide relevant ads based on your preferences.</li>
    <li>Third-Party Vendors: To provide the merchant’s URL and contact details related to your transactions.</li>
    <li>App Improvement Services: If you use the Pro feature, we may analyze transaction and location data to improve tax and tip estimation accuracy.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Your Choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Advertising:</strong> You can choose to remove ads by purchasing the premium version of the app.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Location Data:</strong> You may disable location services on your device, but some features of the app, such as auto-populating merchant information and Pro feature tax calculations, may not work.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
  <p>
    We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no security system is impenetrable.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      For Split Payment transactions, the generated Venmo payment link is stored securely on our server for 7 days to provide user access. After 7 days, the link and associated data are permanently deleted.
    </li>
    <li>
      We do not sell or share this data with any third parties.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to delete the app at any time.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted in the app, and your continued use of the app signifies your acceptance of these changes.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@shopatezlife.com">info@shopatezlife.com</a>.
  </p>
